  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.util.Observer, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants, PTDBBasicFrame

    public class SearchResultsFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements java.util.Observer, PTDBBasicFrame
    An extended JFrame displaying all search results in a scroll panel. Each search result is contained in a SearchResultPanel. This is also an observer of the SearchResultsBuffer, where it can get search results on the fly by calling getResults(). The _cancelButton will notify the search classes that the search has been canceled.
